Class Report

java.lang.Object
logic.Report
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
IncomeReport, OrderReport, PerformanceReport, QuarterReport
public abstract class Report extends Object implements Serializable
The Report class serves as an abstract base class for various types of reports.
